{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"91226f1571","title":"在中文系辩论会上的发言","origin":"北京大学社会主义思想教育委员会编印《北京大学右派分子反动言论汇集》，一九五七年十月。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"10796804e6","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":7,"articleId":"91226f1571"}],"tags":[{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"19f3f1b8ea","name":"北京大学"},{"id":"5cd6c93a1b","name":"张丽中"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3cae7e813c","type":"title","text":"在中文系辩论会上的发言","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"91226f1571"},{"id":"f5ce29da64","type":"authors","text":"北京大学张景中","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"91226f1571"},{"id":"7a7568f7c5","type":"subtitle","text":"张景中在6月7日中文系一年级举办的辩论会上的发言","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"91226f1571"},{"id":"c488167dae","type":"paragraph","text":"根源是某些社会制度。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"91226f1571"},{"id":"f97d8b5cf1","type":"paragraph","text":"三害根源是教条主义，毛主席说：实践——认识——再实践——再认识。如果不由这一实践到另一实践，就会犯教条主义的错误，在胜利的基础上得出的理论不发展就会犯教条主义。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"91226f1571"},{"id":"625c35f46b","type":"paragraph","text":"我们指的制度是社会主义制度的某些环节。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"91226f1571"},{"id":"4ae58824cc","type":"appellation","text":"到处无原则的强调民主集中制，过去破坏法制的行为很多，主要的要从扩大社会主义民主，健全社会主义法制来根除三害。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"91226f1571"}],"page":{"id":"2514fb7805","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"91226f1571","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}